Package com.onarandombox.multiverseinventories.share

Class SharableGroup

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.onarandombox.multiverseinventories.share.SharableGroup
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Shares, java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Iterable<Sharable>, java.util.Collection<Sharable>, java.util.Set<Sharable>
    public final class SharableGroup
extends java.lang.Object
implements Shares
    This class represents a grouping of Sharable objects for the sole purpose of being able to use one keyword in group setups to indicate multiple Sharables.
